+## 2026-07-16 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S1-P01-T010 (read-only /build.json + footer build id; PRODUCTION)
+
+- Tenth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S1-P01), one task per run. Goal: let both domains and test tools confirm the actual running build. Surgical additive change to deploy/cloudflare/worker_cloud.js (+7/-1): a BUILD constant, a read-only /build.json route, and a footer build id link -- NOTHING else touched (six themes, hero videos, cosmic dashboard, fx layers, ChatGPT deep-dive, CSP, no-store all preserved). build_id/source_sha256 are a self-excluding hash (reset the two field values to '0'*12 and '0'*64 and sha256 the file to reproduce source_sha256). Deployed to Cloudflare adp-cloud: pre-deploy version 455afd98 (rollback target) -> post-deploy version 3816d21c, both domains + cron 30 20 * * * preserved. release_mode PRODUCTION. Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S1-P01-T010/test-results/deploy_verify.txt): /build.json is byte-identical across adp.linzezhang.com and adp-cloud.linzezhang35.workers.dev ({"build_id":"bd67a78020a3","source_sha256":"bd67a78020a3...ead084","schema_version":"cn_v0_3","built_at":"2026-07-16"}); build id, bundle/source hash, and schema version match across both domains; no secret is exposed (scan clean); all 7 routes return 200 on both domains; and the protected baseline is intact on both domains (six themes 6/6, three hero videos, cosmic dashboard, fx ambient layers, ChatGPT deep-dive). PARAM-ADP-1124 (cloud abstain threshold 59.6, read by worker_cloud.js) re-attested unchanged with version tag adp-v03-j5-cloud-v10. Rollback: wrangler versions deploy 455afd98 (additive-only, no schema/data change). S1 value: both domains can confirm the exact live build (supports FACT-014). Cost: new_requests = tiny read-only /build.json, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0; recurring cloud cost delta ~$0 (Free tier). Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-16 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S1-P01-T009 (Deployment Manifest Schema; S1 begins)
 
 - Ninth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program and the first of Stage S1 (Truth & Content Stabilization), one task per run. Goal: bind commit + Worker + schema + source + parser + prompt + model + cron into one rebuildable manifest. NOT_DEPLOYED, 0 recurring cloud cost; the generator is read-only and touches nothing in the worker/D1/production. Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/: schemas/deployment_manifest.schema.json (draft-07), tools/generate_manifest.py (deterministic generator with built-in secret redaction), and deployment_manifest.sample.json (content_hash sha256:810a0a1b...). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S1-P01-T009/test-results/manifest_selftest.txt): two clean builds on the same commit produce an identical content_hash (sha256:810a0a1bf416...ba610) and identical binding after removing the allowed-to-vary fields generated_at/generator_note -> DETERMINISTIC; jsonschema.validate(sample, schema) = PASS; the content_hash is computed over the binding object only (independent recompute matches); and redact() masks Bearer/token/40+hex secrets while the manifest stores file sha256 hashes, never file contents, so no secret can leak. The manifest binds 8 components / 9 files (worker_cloud.js, wrangler_cloud.jsonc, schema_cloud.sql with its 8 cn_* tables, boards_v0_3.yaml registry boards-v03-2, owner_controls.yaml, thresholds_v0_3.yaml, MODEL_SPEC.md, formula_registry.yaml, parameter_registry.csv) plus commit and cron 30 20 * * *. S1 value: a single production truth that can be rebuilt and diffed. Cost itemized (unknown != 0): new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0, human = re-run the generator per deploy. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
